Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:35.61,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}僅僅為了尋求奇跡的降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.81,0:01:40.66,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}彷徨於無盡的黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.01,0:01:44.53,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}身陷於此
