Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:54.17,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}今宵明月邀我為伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:56.81,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}即便仍道不出口
